Title: Insecure Defaults Leads to Potential MITM
Description: ezseed-transmission downloads a script from `http://stedolan.github.io/jq/download/linux64/jq` without checking the certificate. An attacker on the same network or on an ISP level could intercept the traffic and push their own version of the file, causing the attackers code to be executed.
AffectedVersions: All versions starting from 0.0.10 up to 0.0.14
